Class TreeNode<T>

java.lang.Object
TreeNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of data to be stored by the Tree Node, a String for the Morse Code Tree implementation
public class TreeNode<T> extends Object
This class is a simple data storing class which holds a reference to a data value as well as a reference to two child nodes, a left and right child. This class will mostly be used for the implementation of a Binary Search Tree, holding letter values
Author:
Evan Song
